put say /proudly We weren't warriors, we weren't leaders and we weren't hunters. We were the unsung heroes of Odcoru and beyond, the silent, the swift. My family were the scouts, the first to move ahead, the first to figure out where to hunt and often the first to fall. But, our names are not in the tales of the heroes, and I think it's important that we remember them. So, as the last of my family line, I have a story of these scouts and if any of your families were also among our ranks, I hope I do yours honor as well.

