put recite The Alpha continued, "There are rumors of dead warriors rising again after falling on the battlefield, only they are twisted and corrupted. They fight now for the enemy.\; There are warnings of magics being used, so foul that they taint the land itself.\; We have been instructed to begin moving East. All tribes are to meet and make the migration together." \; His voice lowered as he gave the command his scouts knew was coming, "My trusted scouts, your time has come again. I ask of you more than I have ever asked before.\; "I need a contingency to go west towards Odcoru, meet their scouts on the path and make sure it is safe.\; Another I need to check to the East and ensure there is a clear way out, know where the water and the food on the path can be found.

